---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Custom Website Development">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-laptop"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Tailored Websites Built from Scratch</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies combines the highest levels of know-how and experience to deliver premium custom web development services that match your requirements exactly. We believe in giving every client a website that is a true, accurate representation of their business — built from scratch, never from templates.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-building"></i></div>
            <h5>Corporate Websites</h5>
            <p>Professional corporate websites that reflect your business identity, engage your audience and establish your credibility online.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i></div>
            <h5>E-commerce Platforms</h5>
            <p>Fully functional e-commerce platforms with shopping carts, product catalogues, payment gateways and order management.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-columns"></i></div>
            <h5>Web Portals &amp; CMS</h5>
            <p>Feature-rich web portals and custom content management systems that are easy for non-technical users to update and manage.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-mobile"></i></div>
            <h5>Mobile Solutions</h5>
            <p>Responsive mobile-friendly websites and custom mobile solutions designed to work beautifully across all screen sizes and devices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i></div>
            <h5>Custom Design</h5>
            <p>Custom theme design, rich internet application design, social media website design and unique logo design that sets you apart.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-shield"></i></div>
            <h5>SEO &amp; W3C Compliant</h5>
            <p>SEO-compatible, W3C-compliant solutions with extensive testing, innovative design, complete tech support and thorough maintenance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
